Subject: [PATCH] Integrate WP-2/3 marketplace alongside the Founding Dealer
 landing page
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

- 11 marketplace routes in app/(marketplace)/ route group (URLs unchanged,
  homepage and root layout untouched)
- Lead engine, AI draft-not-send boundary, funnel metrics, Supabase layer,
  WP-1 migrations
- All UI restyled to the live design system (slate/orange, live form
  vocabulary); globals.css untouched
- Edge middleware.ts for Supabase session refresh, scoped to marketplace
  routes only — / and /api/lead not matched
- Landing form's honeypot + rate-limit posture extended to the new public
  forms (lib/security.ts)
- Gates: tsc clean, 11/11 logic checks, next build + OpenNext Workers
  bundle green

See docs/marketplace-integration.md for the full review map.
